                        text="&lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;/sustainability/abbvie-foundation/addressing-systemic-barriers.html&quot;>Learn more about the AbbVie Foundation’s efforts to address systemic barriers.&lt;/a>&lt;/p>"/>
                </block_11>
